result.name: 梵 BON Japanese Yakitori

reviews.text: A yakitori restaurant with most food of chicken. Fair quality with a bit high price. Service is good
Good food, nice environment. Value for money.

Very delicious that is more than Japanese yakitori restaurant in Japan. HKD400 for 8 piece course include appetizer, rice and dessert exclude service & tax. There is one private room for 4 to 6 person. If you are couple, counter bar is also good with looking cook.

Very decent and authentic Japanese yakitori restaurant. The restaurant design is a long bar table with everyone facing the chef/cooking area which is quite open. Skewers are all very nice, each portion is small though. Can see a lot of Japanese customers.

Good view. Good service and environment. But for the food quality most of the dishes was sort of overwhelmed by the amount of sauce the chefs decide to incorporate with the dish. I would recommend you to tell them in advance to ton down on the sauces. Also for a yakitori joint it is not cheap but at the same time justified due to the environment and views.

reviews.text: A yakitori restaurant with most food of chicken. Fair quality with a bit high price. Service is good

食物一流，服務九流
三個人埋單千三，唔算好貴，但都唔係茶餐廳價，但個waitress 啲skill仲差過茶記，落哂單之後我地傾緊計，無啦啦又番黎，唔好意思都無句，就話頭先你落單既野食，A會生生地，然後B又會生生地，然後C，D，E又要揀鹽燒定醬燒，依啲野唔係落單時問既咩?
跟住落完單我繼續拎住個Menu,然後因為要拎野就暫時放番係枱面，個waitress係一聲都無出攝過黎拎走我份menu，然後放係我隔離，for what,同唔駛問下人係咪已經睇完?！啲咁既服務完全每間野降哂分
Good food, nice environment. Value for money.
日本主廚辭工返日本去了😭味道完全改變，醬也淋超級過分多，難以下嚥，上菜也超慢，真是可惜了⋯⋯希望日本主廚能回來⋯
